{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e47b0b9c2f","title":"谢富治在北京工代会传达周恩来江青对抓“五·一六”的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a5048da76c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":4,"articleId":"e47b0b9c2f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"a0d5508956","name":"清查五·一六","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1a5c822699","type":"title","text":"谢富治在北京工代会传达周恩来江青对抓“五·一六”的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e47b0b9c2f"},{"id":"fafd8316c3","type":"paragraph","text":"谢富治说：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e47b0b9c2f"},{"id":"88f7e15252","type":"paragraph","text":"“抓5.16到处乱抓。在接见工代会第一天会议上，江青同志还讲了话，这个没有向大家传达，也应该告诉同志们。”“江青同志说：不要到处抓5.16，哪里有那么多5.16呢？总理也说：不要借题发挥。江青同志还在会上讲：不要什么都扣5.16的帽子。”","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e47b0b9c2f"}],"page":{"id":"2dfd3ddacf","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e47b0b9c2f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}